        <description>&lt;i&gt;Microx&lt;/i&gt; is a puzzle-board educational game. The player's goal is to arrange a set of chemical element atoms into a predefined pattern to make certain substances before the time runs out. The correct pattern is is displayed at the beginning of each level. At the end of each level the game asks a question related to the arranged pattern. Good answer means progress to the next level.</description>
